OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FGovernment plans to abolish scores of
OL,7,Flocal authorities in the South of
OL,8,FEngland are expected to initially cost
OL,9,Fcouncils more than #12 million over
OL,10,Ftwo years, according to figures
OL,11,Fobtained by ITV News Meridian.
OL,13,FMinisters are replacing district and
OL,14,Fcounty councils in the region with a
OL,15,Fhandful of so-called "mega councils",
OL,16,Fin the biggest shake-up of local
OL,17,Fgovernment in decades. The plans will
OL,18,Falso see devolution to new elected
OL,19,Fmayors.
OL,26,@wD@VOUwD@dO]
