OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FThe new unitary authorities would have
OL,7,Fresponsibility over everything from
OL,8,Fbin collections to adult social care.
OL,9,FBut the system would mean fewer
OL,10,Felected councillors for each local
OL,11,Farea.
OL,13,FThe existing councils in Essex, Kent,
OL,14,FSussex, Surrey, Oxfordshire, Hampshire
OL,15,Fand the Isle of Wight have already
OL,16,Fspent #1.05 million planning for local
OL,17,Fgovernment reorganisation in 2024/25.
