OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FThose authorities have currently
OL,7,Fbudgeted a further #11.22 million for
OL,8,Fcosts associated with the project in
OL,9,F2025/26, according to figures obtained
OL,10,Fvia Freedom of Information (FOI)
OL,11,Frequests.
OL,13,FIn response, the government insisted
OL,14,Fthat abolishing two-tier local
OL,15,Fgovernment across England would "set
OL,16,Fup strong unitary councils" that would
OL,17,Fprovide "better value for money for
OL,18,Ftaxpayers" and "better public
OL,19,Fservices".
