OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FBut Liberal Democrat MP for Horsham,
OL,7,FJohn Milne, said the sums revealed by
OL,8,Fthe ITV News investigation were "very
OL,9,Fhigh" and "quite alarming".
OL,11,FThe former deputy council leader
OL,12,Fadded: "This is just the early days...
OL,13,Fdrawing up business models, doing
OL,14,Fconsultations. So, where we're going
OL,15,Fto go eventually with this is a
OL,16,Ffrightening thing indeed."
