OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FCouncils in Hampshire plan to
OL,7,Fcollectively spend more than #1m over
OL,8,Ftwo years, according to calculations
OL,9,Fof official figures made by ITV News
OL,10,FMeridian.
OL,12,FThe equivalent total for authorities
OL,13,Fin Essex is #2.8m, in Sussex it's
OL,14,F#920,000, while in Kent it's #440,000.
OL,16,FExperts suggest the final bill will
OL,17,Flikely be far higher, with Surrey
OL,18,FCounty Council alone suggesting the
OL,19,Fchanges might cost it #30 million
OL,20,F"over the medium term".
