OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FTest Valley Borough Council alone has
OL,7,Fbudgeted #470,000 for the project in
OL,8,F2025/26, with the Kent borough
OL,9,Fcouncils of Maidstone, Swale and
OL,10,FTunbridge Wells setting annual budgets
OL,11,Fof more than #100,000 each.
OL,13,FBrighton and Hove City Council ` which
OL,14,Fis already a unitary authority `
OL,15,Fexpects to spend more than #350,000 on
OL,16,Fthe changes.
OL,18,FThe county and district councils of
OL,19,FWest Sussex have budgeted #515,000
OL,20,Fover the same period.
