OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FCentral government has provided grants
OL,7,Fto local councils to cover some of the
OL,8,Fcost of planning for the changes.
OL,10,FSeveral councils have earmarked
OL,11,Fproportions of their cash reserves to
OL,12,Ffoot the bill.
OL,14,F"The government have given us some
OL,15,Fmoney to help along the way," said
OL,16,FCllr Paul Harvey, the leader of
OL,17,FBasingstoke & Deane Borough Council.
OL,18,F"We would like more... because these
OL,19,Fare not easy things to do."
