OL,6,FCllr Harvey, who is also Vice-Chair of
OL,7,Fthe District Councils' Network, argued
OL,8,Fthere is a "real danger" in believing
OL,9,F"bigger is better" when it comes to
OL,10,Fthe size of local authorities.
OL,12,F"What we don't want are mega councils
OL,13,Fthat cover huge geographies that lose
OL,14,Fconnection with residents and that
OL,15,Fisn't really local government," Cllr
OL,16,FHarvey added.
