OL,6,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,7,Fand Local Government spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have provided councils in
OL,9,FSussex #1.99bn in 25/26 in Core
OL,10,FSpending Power.
OL,12,F"By abolishing two-tier local
OL,13,Fgovernment across England we will set
OL,14,Fup strong unitary councils that will
OL,15,Fgrow the economy and help local
OL,16,Fleaders get things done.
OL,18,F"This means better value for money for
OL,19,Ftaxpayers and better public services
OL,20,Ffor local residents across the South
OL,21,FEast."
