OL,6,FBut Prof Colin Copus, emeritus
OL,7,Fprofessor at De Montfort University,
OL,8,Fsuggested that there's a "real fallacy
OL,9,Fat the heart of the government's
OL,10,Fargument".
OL,12,F"We've known from 50 years of
OL,13,Findependent academic research, that if
OL,14,Fyou increase the size of local
OL,15,Fgovernment, it is no guarantee that it
OL,16,Fwill be more efficient, more
OL,17,Feffective, better or cheaper, in any
OL,18,Fway".
