OL,3,C'Mega councils' to cost an initial #12
OL,4,Cmillion in the South of England
OL,6,FThe council shake-up comes at the same
OL,7,Ftime as parts of the South prepare for
OL,8,Fgreater devolution of powers from
OL,9,FWestminster, with elected mayors
OL,10,Fplanned in 'Greater Essex', 'Sussex
OL,11,Fand Brighton' and 'Hampshire and the
OL,12,FSolent'.
OL,14,FLocal elections are due to take place
OL,15,Fin many of the affected areas in May
OL,16,F2026, although this is yet to be
OL,17,Fconfirmed by ministers. Final
OL,18,Fdecisions on the new council
OL,19,Fboundaries have yet to be made.
